---
// Colaboraciones.astro
---

<!-- Recent Works & Collaborations (Reformatted) -->
<section class="py-32" id="collab">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-start items-end mb-20 gap-4 w-full">
        <div class="w-full text-left">
            <h2 class="font-headline text-5xl font-light text-on-surface">Colaboraciones</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Carousel Area (Left) -->
        <div class="md:col-span-7 bg-surface-container-low shadow-xl group relative carousel-container">
            <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-[4/5]">
                <div class="carousel-track h-full scroll-smooth">
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img alt="Drag Item 1" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-all duration-700" src="/img-col-car-1/f1.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img alt="Drag Item 2" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-all duration-700" src="/img-col-car-1/f2.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img alt="Drag Item 3" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-all duration-700" src="/img-col-car-1/f3.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img alt="Drag Item 4" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-all duration-700" src="/img-col-car-1/f4.png" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Controls -->
                <button
                    class="absolute z-10 top-1/2 left-4 -translate-y-1/2 bg-white/50 hover:bg-white rounded-full p-3 text-black transition-colors opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 carousel-prev"
                    aria-label="Anterior">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span>
                </button>
                <button
                    class="absolute z-10 top-1/2 right-4 -translate-y-1/2 bg-white/50 hover:bg-white rounded-full p-3 text-black transition-colors opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 carousel-next"
                    aria-label="Siguiente">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Text Area (Right) -->
        <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col items-start gap-8 pr-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                <h3 class="font-headline text-5xl leading-tight font-light text-on-surface italic">Alei X Springfield</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="font-body text-lg text-secondary leading-relaxed">
                Una colaboración que fusiona la estética de Springfield con la visión artística de Alei, creando una serie de obras que exploran la cultura pop a través de un lente artístico contemporáneo.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

